<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: Arial; background:#f5f5f5; padding:20px;">
  <div style="max-width:600px; background:#fff; margin:auto; padding:20px; border-radius:8px;">
    
    <div style="text-align:center;">
      <img src="<%= logoUrl %>" width="150" />
    </div>

    <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>

    <p>Your payment has been successfully received 🎉</p>

    <p><strong>Order ID:</strong> <%= orderId %></p>
    <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> $<%= total %></p>
    <p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> <%= paymentMethod %></p>

    <p>We are now preparing your order.</p>

    <p>Thank you for shopping with Shoptoo!</p>

  </div>
</body>
</html>